@startuml deployment
!theme plain
title Deployment Diagram\nClient-Server Architecture (Ch.6, Slide 28)

node "CLIENT SIDE" as client_side #E3F2FD {
  node "Web Browser" as browser {
    component "Next.js Frontend\n(SSR + CSR)" as nextjs
    component "Google Maps JS\nAPI Client" as gmaps_client
  }
}

node "SERVER SIDE" as server_side #FFF8E1 {
  node "Backend Server" as backend {
    component "FastAPI\n(Uvicorn ASGI)" as fastapi
    component "SQLModel ORM" as orm
    component "Alembic\n(Migrations)" as alembic
  }

  database "PostgreSQL" as db {
    storage "13 tables\n(16 domain classes)" as tables
  }
}

cloud "External Services" as ext {
  component "Google Maps\nPlatform API" as gmaps_api
  component "OCPP Hardware\n(Simulated)" as ocpp
}

nextjs -down-> fastapi : HTTP/REST API\n(JSON over HTTPS)\nJWT Bearer Token
gmaps_client -right-> gmaps_api : Maps JS API
fastapi -down-> orm
orm -down-> db : SQL (Connection Pool)
alembic -down-> db : DDL migrations
fastapi ..> ocpp : OCPP 1.6/2.0 (Simulated)

note bottom of client_side
  <b>Client (Ch.6, Slide 28)</b>
  - Browser'da calisir
  - UI rendering, kullanici etkilesimi
  - Dev: npm run dev (port 3000)
end note

note bottom of server_side
  <b>Server (Ch.6, Slide 28)</b>
  - Backend sunucuda calisir
  - Layered Architecture (4 katman)
  - Dev: uvicorn (port 8000)
  - DB: docker postgres:16 (port 5432)
end note

@enduml
